<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<style>
@page { size: A4; margin: 25mm 20mm 18mm 20mm; }

body {
  font-family: "Malgun Gothic", "Batang", sans-serif;
  font-size: 11pt;
  color: #000;
  margin: 0;
}

h1 {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 20pt;
  letter-spacing: 0.35em;
  margin: 0 0 32px 0;
}

table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  table-layout: fixed;
}

td, th {
  border: 1px solid #000;
  padding: 6px 8px;
  font-weight: normal;
  vertical-align: middle;
}

.center { text-align: center; }
.left { text-align: left; }
.top { vertical-align: top; }

.label { width: 26%; }
.sub { width: 13%; }

.title-row { height: 48px; }
.party-row { height: 49px; }
.opinion-row { height: 188px; }
.other-row { min-height: 67px; height: auto; }

.other-cell .attachment-images {
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.other-cell .attachment-item {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  page-break-inside: avoid;
}

.other-cell .attachment-caption {
  font-size: 9pt;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.other-cell .attachment-images img {
  display: block;
  max-width: 100%;
  max-height: 240px;
  width: auto;
  height: auto;
}

.legal-row {
  height: 210px;
  vertical-align: top;
  padding: 14px 0 0 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
}

.legal-text {
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}

.date {
  text-align: center;
  letter-spacing: 1.2em;
  margin: 18px 0 18px 0;
}

.info-line {
  position: relative;
  height: 28px;
  padding: 0 0;
}

.phone {
  text-align: right;
  padding-right: 28px;
}

.name-line {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 170px;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

.recipient {
  text-align: right;
  padding-right: 36px;
  margin-top: 6px;
}

.note-label {
  width: 26%;
  text-align: center;
}

.note-cell {
  font-size: 10pt;
  line-height: 1.55;
  padding: 14px 8px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<h1>의견제출서</h1>

<table>
  <tr class="title-row">
    <td class="label center">1. 예정된 처분의 제목</td>
    <td colspan="3">{{ disposition_title | nl2br }}</td>
  </tr>

  <tr class="party-row">
    <td rowspan="2" class="label center">2. 당사자</td>
    <td class="sub center">성명(명칭)</td>
    <td colspan="2">{{ submitter_name | default('', true) }}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr class="party-row">
    <td class="sub center">주소</td>
    <td colspan="2">{{ submitter_address | default('', true) }}</td>
  </tr>

  <tr class="opinion-row">
    <td class="label center">3. 의&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;견</td>
    <td colspan="3" class="top">{{ opinion | nl2br }}</td>
  </tr>

  <tr class="other-row">
    <td class="label center">4. 기&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;타</td>
    <td colspan="3" class="top other-cell">
      {{ other | nl2br }}
      {% if attachment_images %}
      <div class="attachment-images">
        {% for img in attachment_images %}
        <div class="attachment-item">
          {% if img.caption %}<div class="attachment-caption">{{ img.caption }}</div>{% endif %}
          <img src="{{ img.data_uri | safe }}" alt="{{ img.caption }}" />
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td colspan="4" class="legal-row">
      <div class="legal-text">
        행정절차법 제27조제1항(제31조제3항)의 규정에 의하여 위와 같이 의견을 제출합니다.
      </div>

      <div class="date">{{ written_date }}</div>

      <div class="info-line">
        의견제출인 주소&nbsp;&nbsp;{{ submitter_address_footer | default('', true) }}
      </div>

      <div class="info-line phone">
        (전화:&nbsp;&nbsp;{{ submitter_phone | default('', true) }})
      </div>

      <div class="name-line">
        <span>성명&nbsp;&nbsp;{{ submitter_name_footer | default('', true) }}</span>
        <span>(서명 또는 인)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="recipient">귀하</div>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td class="note-label">비<br/>고</td>
    <td colspan="3" class="note-cell">
      1. 기재란이 부족한 경우에는 별지를 사용하실 수 있습니다.<br/>
      2. 증거자료 등을 첨부하실 수 있습니다.<br/>
      3. 위 의견제출과 관련하여 문서를 받으신 경우에는 문서번호와 일자를<br/>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;제1호에 함께 기재해 주시기 바랍니다.
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>